    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Language-Aware Router\\n\",\"**NLP Project 70 of 100** — Detect language, then route to the correct NLP pipeline.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess,sys,importlib\\nfor pkg in ['langdetect']:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','pip','install','-q',pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from langdetect import detect\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Define language-specific pipelines\\ndef english_pipeline(text): return f'[EN] Processing: {text[:50]}... → Sentiment: positive'\\ndef spanish_pipeline(text): return f'[ES] Procesando: {text[:50]}... → Sentimiento: positivo'\\ndef french_pipeline(text): return f'[FR] Traitement: {text[:50]}... → Sentiment: positif'\\ndef default_pipeline(text): return f'[??] Unknown language for: {text[:50]}...'\\n\\nROUTES = {'en': english_pipeline, 'es': spanish_pipeline, 'fr': french_pipeline}\\n\\ndef language_router(text):\\n    try:\\n        lang = detect(text)\\n    except:\\n        lang = 'unknown'\\n    handler = ROUTES.get(lang, default_pipeline)\\n    return lang, handler(text)\\n\\ntexts = [\\n    'I love this product, it works perfectly!',\\n    'Me encanta este producto, funciona perfectamente!',\\n    'J\\\\'adore ce produit, il fonctionne parfaitement!',\\n    'Ich liebe dieses Produkt, es funktioniert perfekt!',\\n    'Este produto é incrível e funciona bem!',\\n]\\n\\nfor text in texts:\\n    lang, result = language_router(text)\\n    print(f'Detected: {lang:3s} | {result}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Language detection routes text** to the appropriate processing pipeline.\\n\",\"- **langdetect handles major languages well** but struggles with very short text.\\n\",\"- **Unknown languages get a fallback handler** to avoid silent failures.\\n\",\"- **For production, use fasttext language detection** for better short-text accuracy.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
